OL,3,CSouth East Water to undergo 'MOT' as
OL,4,Cplans for new regulator unveiled
OL,6,FWater companies will be required to
OL,7,Fcarry out to infrastructure "MOTs" to
OL,8,Fprevent major failures under plans for
OL,9,Fa new industry watchdog, the
OL,10,FGovernment has said.
OL,12,FAt the height of the incident, the
OL,13,Fcompany reported that 30,000 customers
OL,14,Facross the two counties were without
OL,15,Fwater, or experiencing low water
OL,16,Fpressure.
