OL,3,CSouth East Water to undergo 'MOT' as
OL,4,Cplans for new regulator unveiled
OL,6,FThe beleaguered water firm has faced
OL,7,Fheavy criticism from MPs and the
OL,8,Fpublic as the outage came on the heels
OL,9,Fof a similar incident last month,
OL,10,Fwhere 24,000 people in Tunbridge Wells
OL,11,Fwere left without drinking water for
OL,12,Ftwo weeks.
OL,14,FMinisters are set to unveil a series
OL,15,Fof reforms in Parliament as they move
OL,16,Fahead with a major regulatory shake-up
OL,17,Fthat will see Ofwat abolished and the
OL,18,Fcurrent system of overlapping
OL,19,Foversight by four different bodies
OL,20,Fmerged into a single regulator.
