OL,3,CSouth East Water to undergo 'MOT' as
OL,4,Cplans for new regulator unveiled
OL,6,FThe Water White Paper, published this
OL,7,Fmorning, will outline powers planned
OL,8,Ffor this new watchdog, which aim to
OL,9,Fput failure prevention first and
OL,10,Fstrengthen accountability.
OL,12,FUnder the proposals, water companies
OL,13,Fwill have to perform health checks on
OL,14,Ftheir infrastructure to proactively
OL,15,Fidentify crumbling pipes, pumps or
OL,16,Fissues at sewage treatment works
OL,17,Fbefore they fail.
