OL,3,CSouth East Water to undergo 'MOT' as
OL,4,Cplans for new regulator unveiled
OL,6,FThe hope is that risks such as South
OL,7,FEast Water's pipes bursting in cold
OL,8,Fweather, which recently left thousands
OL,9,Fof homes without supply, are
OL,10,Fidentified in advance.
OL,12,FA chief engineer will also sit inside
OL,13,Fthe new water regulator for the first
OL,14,Ftime in two decades to bring back
OL,15,Fhands-on checks of infrastructure, so
OL,16,Fthat firms "are not marking their own
OL,17,Fhomework".
