OL,3,CSouth East Water to undergo 'MOT' as
OL,4,Cplans for new regulator unveiled
OL,6,FOfwat will unlikely be formally axed
OL,7,Fbefore 2027, and the process to
OL,8,Festablish the new regulator will be
OL,9,Fcomplex ` meaning it is unclear when
OL,10,Fit will start operating.
OL,12,FBut the Government will say on Tuesday
OL,13,Fthat it will set out a transition path
OL,14,Fin the coming months, and a new water
OL,15,Freform bill to bring forward the
OL,16,Flegislation needed for the system to
OL,17,Ftake effect.
