OL,3,CSouth East Water to undergo 'MOT' as
OL,4,Cplans for new regulator unveiled
OL,6,FEnvironment Secretary Emma Reynolds
OL,7,Fsaid: "These are once-in-a-generation
OL,8,Freforms for our water system ` tough
OL,9,Foversight, real accountability, and no
OL,10,Fmore excuses.
OL,12,F"Water companies will have nowhere to
OL,13,Fhide from poor performance, customers
OL,14,Fwill get the service they deserve, and
OL,15,Finvestors will see a system built for
OL,16,Fthe future.
OL,18,F"This builds on the tough action we've
OL,19,Falready delivered, from record
OL,20,Finvestment to banning unfair bonuses."
