OL,3,CSouth East Water to undergo 'MOT' as
OL,4,Cplans for new regulator unveiled
OL,6,FThis will replace the current "one-
OL,7,Fsize-fits-all" approach, with the aim
OL,8,Fof providing the new regulator with a
OL,9,Fbetter understanding of how each firm
OL,10,Foperates.
OL,12,FAnd where their performance falls
OL,13,Fshort, the regulator will be able to
OL,14,Fput tailored "performance improvement
OL,15,Fregimes" in place, which means it can
OL,16,Fact quicker to fix failures.
