OL,4,Cplans for new regulator unveiled
OL,6,FElsewhere, the paper outlines new "no-
OL,7,Fnotice" powers for the watchdog to
OL,8,Fcheck water firms' security and
OL,9,Femergency preparedness for events such
OL,10,Fas attacks on infrastructure or
OL,11,Fcontingency plans for supply issues.
OL,13,FClean lines of accountability for
OL,14,Fsenior executives will also be
OL,15,Foutlined in the paper in measures
OL,16,Flikened to those seen in the financial
OL,17,Fsector.
