OL,6,FPhilip Duffy, chief executive of the
OL,7,FEnvironment Agency, called the Water
OL,8,FWhite Paper "a key milestone in
OL,9,Fturning around our water system".
OL,11,F"During the transition to the new
OL,12,Fregulator, our priorities remain
OL,13,Funchanged," he said.
