OL,3,CSouth East Water to undergo 'MOT' as
OL,4,Cplans for new regulator unveiled
OL,6,F"We are focused on delivering our key
OL,7,Fservices ` carrying out 10,000
OL,8,Finspections of water company assets
OL,9,Fthis year and working with our partner
OL,10,Fregulators, planners, water companies,
OL,11,Ffarmers and environmental
OL,12,Forganisations to protect and enhance
OL,13,Four water environment."
OL,15,FChris Walters, Ofwat interim chief
OL,16,Fexecutive, said: "The creation of a
OL,17,Fnew water regulator for England will
OL,18,Fbring a renewed focus, improve the
OL,19,Fsector for customers, investors and
OL,20,Fthe environment, and rebuild trust.
