OL,6,F"In the meantime, our work continues.
OL,8,F"We are already working closely with
OL,9,F(the Environment Department) and our
OL,10,Fpartner regulators as the Government
OL,11,Fdevelops the new body, ensuring the
OL,12,Fsector moves towards a more integrated
OL,13,Fand resilient future."
OL,15,FTim Farron, environment spokesperson
OL,16,Ffor the Liberal Democrats, said the
OL,17,FWhite Paper "does not go far enough to
OL,18,Fguarantee the fundamental regulatory
OL,19,Freform that was promised".
