OL,6,F"We must completely overhaul how water
OL,7,Fcompanies run," he said.
OL,9,FJames Wallace, chief executive of
OL,10,FRiver Action, said many of the
OL,11,Fmeasures announced are "welcome
OL,12,Fsteps", but warned that "major gaps
OL,13,Fremain" in areas such as triggers for
OL,14,Fspecial administration, a commitment
OL,15,Fto restructure company investment and
OL,16,Fownership and more ambition to tackle
OL,17,Fagricultural pollution.
