OL,6,F"The publication of the Water White
OL,7,FPaper signals the Government
OL,8,Frecognises the scale of the freshwater
OL,9,Femergency, but lacks the urgency and
OL,10,Fbold reform to tackle it," he said.
OL,12,FA spokesperson for Water UK, which
OL,13,Frepresents the industry, welcomed the
OL,14,FWhite Paper but said the focus "must
OL,15,Fnow shift from diagnosis to delivery".
OL,17,F"Our country will not have the
OL,18,Fenvironment it wants or the economic
OL,19,Fgrowth it needs until a new water
OL,20,Fregulator is established," they said.
